      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "About QA Dashboard",
        "type": "text",
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# QA Dashboard for SDLC\n\nThis dashboard tracks essential QA metrics based on industry standards:\n\n## Primary Metrics:\n- **Escaped Bugs**: Bugs found in production (primary indicator of QA effectiveness)\n- **Test Coverage**: Percentage of requirements covered by tests\n- **Defect Density**: Number of defects per requirement\n- **Test Case Effectiveness**: How effectively tests find defects\n\n## Timeline Analytics:\n- **Development Delay**: Time from requirements published to test case creation\n- **Execution Delay**: Time from test case creation to first execution\n- **Productivity**: Test case creation rate per day\n\n## Scope Change Analysis:\n- **Defect Leakage**: Rate of defects escaping to later stages\n- **Defect Trend**: Historical trends in defect identification\n\n*Data synchronized from Azure DevOps*",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24}
      }
